name: The Unstable Cone: Soft Color Edition
description: The Soft Color Edition Cone is one that I hope brings you light even when life is looking a little dark. I individually chose each color to add in this sequence that provided me with some sort of calming feeling when gazing at it. It's a cone that I hope provides you with the same feeling. I hope you are able to turn your day around if it's a bad one. I hope you are able to talk to someone if you are feeling sad. And I hope you are supported by someone out there. This cone is dedicated to my sister who understands, listens, and supports me through some of the hardest chapters of my life. She's younger than me but far more mature and far beyond more intelligent than her own age prevails. You are the light in my life. I love you to death and back.
